cell2d.space

Class CircleHitbox<T extends CellGame>

  • java.lang.Object
    • cell2d.space.Hitbox<T>
      • cell2d.space.CircleHitbox<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The subclass of CellGame that uses the SpaceStates that can use this CircleHitbox

    public class CircleHitbox<T extends CellGame>
extends Hitbox<T>

    A CircleHitbox is a circular Hitbox with its origin at its center. A CircleHitbox's radius cannot be negative.
